Task - Make a map which displays Country-wise Sales.

Step 1 - Open power bi report
Step 2 - Add 'Map' visual in the power bi report.
To add 'Map', go to Visualization pane -> Drag and drop 'Map' visual in power bi report.


Step 3 - Add fields into the 'Map' visual
Put 'Country' in the Location field and 'Sales' in the Size field.

The size of the bubble will be determined by the number of sales generated by the country.

In this way, we can make and use a point map in the power bi report.

